The 512GB storage is a game-changer. I can store all my favorite apps, media, and files without ever worrying about running out of space. Perfect for work, play, and everything in between!

Overall, the C Idea Adults Tablet has exceeded all my expectations. Its stylish, powerful, and a fantastic value for the price. If youre looking for a tablet that combines performance, storage, and versatility, this is definitely the one to get. Highly recommend!

review_title: Not strong enough and damaged charger cable
review:
It charged my car battery a bit but it wasn't strong enough to get the car started. I had to use this charger until it was completely depleted (I had fully charged it), and still connect jumper cables to another car to start a completely dead battery. It might work better if your battery isn't completely dead but just needs a bit of a top-up to get it started. 
The adapter to charge the battery pack was broken when I received it. I was able to piece it back together but I don't think it will hold up. It didn't come with a UK style plug but a EU type one and one of the prongs had broken off. I wouldn't recommend it.
